(VOCALIZES)

666
00:58:54,822 --> 00:59:01,246
(SINGING) <i>As the close of the fading day</i>

667
00:59:01,621 --> 00:59:05,083
<i>I follow in your footsteps</i>

668
00:59:06,834 --> 00:59:11,089
<i>Without a single word spoken...</i>

669
00:59:54,549 --> 00:59:57,885
JINWOO: <i>I read sound with my eyes.</i>

670
00:59:59,929 --> 01:00:03,558
<i>It means every time I blink,</i>
<i>for a brief moment,</i>

671
